# Awards WON
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
:OneBattleAfterAnother :wonAward :BestPicture .
:PaulThomasAnderson    :wonAward :BestDirector , :BestAdaptedScreenplay .
:MichaelBJordan        :wonAward :BestActor .
:JessieBuckley         :wonAward :BestActress .
:SeanPenn              :wonAward :BestSupportingActor .
