:KPopDemonHunters      :wonAward :BestAnimatedFeature .
:SentimentalValue      :wonAward :BestInternationalFeature .
:MrNobodyAgainstPutin  :wonAward :BestDocumentaryFeature .
:AutumnDuraldArkapaw   :wonAward :BestCinematography .
:LudwigGoransson       :wonAward :BestOriginalScore .
